      <title>美国轰炸机袭击胡塞武装武器储存地点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-bombers-strike-houthi-weapons-storage-sites-in-yemen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士周三晚间称，美国 B-2 隐形轰炸机袭击了也门胡塞叛军有关的武器储存地点，这是美国为阻止伊朗支持的组织发动袭击而采取的最新举措，这些袭击已扰乱了红海的商业航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-bombers-strike-houthi-weapons-storage-sites-in-yemen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国利用间谍手段阻止刚果致命冲突的蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-turns-to-spycraft-to-halt-spread-of-congo-s-deadly-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年 11 月，美国顶级间谍抵达金沙萨，向刚果民主共和国总统费利克斯·齐塞克迪提出一项不同寻常的提议：美国将与刚果民主共和国政府分享秘密情报，作为交换，他必须参与世界上持续时间最长的冲突之一的停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-turns-to-spycraft-to-halt-spread-of-congo-s-deadly-conflict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体预测日本自民党可能自 2009 年以来首次失去多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/japan-s-ldp-may-lose-majority-for-first-time-since-2009-media-forecasts-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本各大媒体周四预测，日本执政党自民党在本月的选举中可能会自2009年以来首次失去众议院的绝对多数席位，但在其联盟伙伴的帮助下仍能保持对众议院的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/japan-s-ldp-may-lose-majority-for-first-time-since-2009-media-forecasts-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:29:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在宪法中将韩国定义为敌对国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/north-korea-defines-south-korea-as-hostile-state-in-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜在其宪法中将韩国定义为“敌对国家”，本周早些时候，平壤炸毁了连接朝鲜半岛南部的部分道路，加剧了两国之间的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/north-korea-defines-south-korea-as-hostile-state-in-constitution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:47:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本薪资协议时间表或将影响日本央行下次加息观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/japan-s-wage-deal-timeline-may-shape-boj-view-on-next-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本能否维持工资增长势头，很可能成为影响日本首相石破茂政府任期以及央行下次加息时机的关键因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/japan-s-wage-deal-timeline-may-shape-boj-view-on-next-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济放缓致日本出口创 2021 年以来最大降幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/japan-exports-unexpectedly-slip-for-first-time-in-10-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本9月份出口创下2021年2月以来最大降幅，随着全球需求减弱，日本经济复苏势头减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/japan-exports-unexpectedly-slip-for-first-time-in-10-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险投资家德雷珀称他曾向哈里斯和特朗普捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/venture-capitalist-draper-says-he-donated-to-harris-and-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒂姆·德雷珀 (Tim Draper) 是一位硅谷风险投资家，以投资太空探索技术公司和 Theranos 等各类初创企业而闻名，他表示自己曾向卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普的美国总统竞选活动捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/venture-capitalist-draper-says-he-donated-to-harris-and-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在福克斯电视台接受采访时发誓要与拜登有所不同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/harris-vows-to-be-different-than-biden-in-fiery-fox-interview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在周三接受福克斯新闻采访时试图转移对政府处理边境危机的方式、她对跨性别权利的立场以及她与总统乔·拜登的关系的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/harris-vows-to-be-different-than-biden-in-fiery-fox-interview</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:14:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>敦促里夫斯无视警告并从富人那里筹集 150 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/reeves-urged-to-ignore-warnings-and-raise-15-billion-from-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家智库的报告称，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）可以通过瞄准资本收益和遗产，每年从英国最富有的人那里筹集 150 亿英镑（200 亿美元），而不会引发百万富翁大批外流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/reeves-urged-to-ignore-warnings-and-raise-15-billion-from-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国家相关机构呼吁调查英特尔安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/china-state-linked-agency-calls-for-probe-into-intel-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国互联网监管机构支持的一家机构正在推动对国内销售的英特尔公司产品进行调查，并警告其存在安全漏洞和高故障率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/china-state-linked-agency-calls-for-probe-into-intel-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 10:54:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
